custom-sql.name: DeviceTypeTree
custom-sql.sql: select c.mrid,a.dtid,a.category,c.mrname,a.name,a.subcategory , a.model,a.objectid,a.logo,a.description from t_manufacturer_info_init c left join (select * from t_device_type_init d,t_category_map_init b where d.category=b.id) a on a.mrid=c.mrid where mrname=:mrName and a.name=:cateName and a.subCategory=:subCategory
